---
title: Grilled Steaks and Charred Jalapeño Chimichurri with Chilean-Inspired Patatas Bravas
description: Charred jalapeño peppers kick things up a notch in a quick chimichurri that's draped over sweet grilled tomatoes and steak! South American-inspired patatas bravas bring a spicy and aromatic quality to this plate perfect for fresco dining!
